Package org.blockchainnative.fabric

Interface FabricSmartContract<TContractType>

  • Type Parameters:
    TContractType - Type parameter representing the actual contract type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    SmartContract<FabricContractInfo<TContractType>>
    public interface FabricSmartContract<TContractType>
extends SmartContract<FabricContractInfo<TContractType>>
    Allows smart contract wrappers to retrieve their contract info.

    The use of this interface is optional, declaring a method named SmartContract.GET_CONTRACT_INFO_METHOD_NAME with the return type of FabricContractInfo (with or without TContractType) will have the same result.

    1.0
